OL,3,CNew Transport Secretary to visit
OL,4,CGreater Manchester's Bee Bus Network
OL,6,FNew Transport Secretary Louise Haigh
OL,7,Fwill visit Greater Manchester's
OL,8,Fpioneering public bus network on
OL,9,FThursday, 11 July, as Labour pledges
OL,10,Fto start a "bus revolution" and allow
OL,11,Fservices to be taken back under local
OL,12,Fpublic control.
OL,14,FMs Haigh will meet Greater Manchester
OL,15,FMayor Andy Burnham to discuss how the
OL,16,Farea's Bee Network can be replicated
OL,17,Facross the country to improve services
OL,18,Fand grow passenger numbers.
