OL,3,CNew Transport Secretary to visit
OL,4,CGreater Manchester's Bee Bus Network
OL,6,FThe Bee Network launched in Wigan,
OL,7,FBolton and parts of Bury, Salford and
OL,8,FManchester in September last year as
OL,9,FGreater Manchester became the first
OL,10,Farea to bring buses under local
OL,11,Fcontrol.
OL,13,FOver the past six months, the number
OL,14,Fof people using buses in those areas
OL,15,Fhas increased by five percent, with
OL,16,Fover 849,000 passenger journeys.
OL,18,FRecord numbers of people are also
OL,19,Ftravelling by tram, with usage up by
OL,20,Fmore than 20 percent over the past
OL,21,Fyear.
