OL,3,CNew Transport Secretary to visit
OL,4,CGreater Manchester's Bee Bus Network
OL,6,FAnd Greater Manchester until recently
OL,7,Fhad 830 bus services run by 30
OL,8,Foperators with 150 different ticket
OL,9,Ftypes with some routes near
OL,10,Funiversities and city and town centres
OL,11,Fover-supplied and more rural areas
OL,12,Funder-supplied.
OL,14,FThe mayor has promised the new system
OL,15,Fwill give public control over fares,
OL,16,Froutes and frequencies, with financial
OL,17,Fpenalties for poor performance written
OL,18,Finto the five-year contracts for
OL,19,Fservices, provided by 50 new electric-
OL,20,Fpowered buses, all with the same Bee
OL,21,FNetwork yellow livery.
