OL,3,CNew Transport Secretary to visit
OL,4,CGreater Manchester's Bee Bus Network
OL,6,FThe new network is currently rolling
OL,7,Fout across the region.
OL,9,FLabour now plans to remove barriers so
OL,10,FLocal Transport Authorities across the
OL,11,Fcountry will be empowered to take back
OL,12,Fcontrol of buses.
OL,14,FMs Haigh said: "Buses are the
OL,15,Flifeblood of communities, but the
OL,16,Fsystem is broken.
OL,18,F"Too often, passengers are left
OL,19,Fwaiting hours for buses that don't
OL,20,Fturn up ` and some have been cut off
OL,21,Faltogether.
OL,26,@vD@POUzD@AOU
