OL,3,CNew Transport Secretary to visit
OL,4,CGreater Manchester's Bee Bus Network
OL,6,F"Change starts now. This new
OL,7,FGovernment will give local leaders the
OL,8,Ftools they need to deliver better
OL,9,Fbuses up and down the country.
OL,11,F"Our plan will create and save vital
OL,12,Fbus routes by giving every community
OL,13,Fthe power to take back control of
OL,14,Ftheir bus services through franchising
OL,15,For public ownership.
OL,17,F"We are already seeing how the Bee
OL,18,FNetwork is delivering for people
OL,19,Facross Greater Manchester ` we will
OL,20,Fensure every community can enjoy the
OL,21,Fsame benefits.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
