OL,3,CNew Transport Secretary to visit
OL,4,CGreater Manchester's Bee Bus Network
OL,6,F"Mr Burnham said: "Properly integrated
OL,7,Fpublic transport is the key to
OL,8,Funlocking growth and opportunity
OL,9,Facross our city-region, improving the
OL,10,Flives of our residents, supporting
OL,11,Fbusinesses and delivering greater
OL,12,Fvalue for money.
OL,14,F"The numbers speak for themselves `
OL,15,Four Bee Network has more passengers
OL,16,Fthan ever before and is providing a
OL,17,Fbetter service for residents.
