OL,3,CNew Transport Secretary to visit
OL,4,CGreater Manchester's Bee Bus Network
OL,6,F"Greater Manchester has shown that our
OL,7,Fpioneering approach works and we look
OL,8,Fforward to working with the Government
OL,9,Fto put power back into the hands of
OL,10,Flocal communities."
OL,12,FThe transport authority now has its
OL,13,Feyes on local railway lines, with
OL,14,Fplans for eight routes to be brought
OL,15,Finto the network. They will include
OL,16,Flines to Wigan, Rochdale, Glossop and
OL,17,FStockport.
